WEBVTT

01:01:50.525 --> 01:01:53.926
<i>Step two.</i>
<i>With the lifeboat</i>
<i>facing into the waves...</i>

01:01:53.928 --> 01:01:58.631
<i>making the ride</i>
<i>as comfortable as possible,</i>
<i>blow your whistle soothingly.</i>

01:01:58.633 --> 01:02:02.001
<i>Step three.</i>
<i>Turn the lifeboat</i>
<i>sideways to the waves...</i>

01:02:02.003 --> 01:02:05.171
<i>accompanied by harsh,</i>
<i>aggressive use</i>
<i>of the whistle.</i>
